Package: segmenTools
Title: Tools for Functional Genome Exploration
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Rainer", "Machne", email = "rainer.machne@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/raim/segmenTools
BugReports: https://github.com/raim/segmenTools/issues
Maintainer: Rainer Machne <rainer.machne@gmail.com>
Description: tools and scripts for functional analysis of genomes, from genomic intervals (e.g. chromosomal domains, transcripts, open reading frames) to genes and single nucleotides.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests:
